## Humanitarian Use Notice

This software is specifically designed for disaster relief and emergency
communication scenarios. The maintainers encourage its use in humanitarian
contexts and provide community support for such deployments.

Organizations using EmergencyBox for disaster relief are encouraged to:
- Share deployment experiences and improvements with the community
- Contribute bug fixes and enhancements back to the project
- Document real-world use cases to improve the system

For commercial deployments in non-emergency contexts, please consider
contributing to the project or sponsoring development.
